Package: semgui
Type: Package
Title: Graphical SEM for Jamovi
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Seiji Shibata
Maintainer: Seiji Shibata <sbtseiji@users.noreply.github.com>
Description: A graphical user interface for structural equation modeling in jamovi.
    Supports CFA, path models, full SEM, higher-order factors, and bifactor models.
    Models are specified by drawing path diagrams and fitted using lavaan.
License: GPL-3.0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: jmvcore (>= 0.8.5), R6, lavaan, jsonlite
